yes, but of course when the RGBox is apart and I need a gasket to put it back 
together I dont want to wait till some time after you get them in next week, 
and then shipping time.  The only LOCAL source who claimed access to them was 
also out of stock., it wasn't worth waiting.  Use those skills you learned in 
kindergarten- tracing shapes and using scissors.

